    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and honestly, it's been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and drives like a dream! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be appreciated just as much. It\u2019s a fantastic ride for anyone looking for something dependable and ready to go. Drop me a message if you want to come see it\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
