    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 996-generation Porsche 911 Carrera, powered by the mid-mounted 3.4L flat-six M96 engine paired with a G96 6-speed manual transaxle. This specimen features a verified IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced Air Oil Separator (AOS), ensuring mechanical longevity. The chassis maintains its factory-spec rigidity with a multi-link rear suspension setup and communicative hydraulic steering. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust with no signs of bore scoring or typical seal leaks. A technically sound platform for the purist seeking an analog performance experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
