    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape, both inside and out! It drives like a dream and has been really well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a solid, dependable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure, this is the one! I've taken great care of it, and it's ready to hit the road. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 34500.0,
